  <brief_title>Retrograde Intrarenal Stone Surgery - A Method of Treating the ESWL Resistant Kidney Stone</brief_title>
  <official_title>RIRS - A Method of Treating the ESWL Resistant Kidney Stone</official_title>
  <sponsors>
